Created an attachment (id=74600)
new patch

Updates:
It mimics the algorithm of the real code and checks for equality between returned values and the valued calculated by the test class.
The test case feeds the tested class with its own Random seed and Gain so it will be able to know the "random" values the tested class use.
If the system variable "comperhensive.test" does not exist or is not equal to "yes" or "true" (case ignored), the test tests only one of every 500 permutations (takes few seconds).
In this mode the test is running on only 288 permutations.

The tests pass on my machine.
